marketing: Shell Gadus S2 V460D 2 grease is a high performance grease for slow moving heavily loaded large bearings subject to shock loads.  It is based on high viscosity index mineral oil and a lithium soap thickener. Apart from containing additives to ensure reliable anti corrosion & anti oxidation performance, it also contains solids to ensure the grease can handle shock loads.
